{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"mem 的小站"}},"post":{"id":"3d3472ba-4912-5781-8d34-e29c88684305","excerpt":"1. 动机 进行 图增强(graph augmentation) 的动机：输入图很难恰好是适宜于 GNN 的最优计算图。 特征层面： 输入图可能缺少特征 特征很难编码 GNN 难以学习到特定的图结构 结构层面： 图过度稀疏：message passing 效率太低——增加虚拟节点/边 图过度稠密：message…","html":"<h2 id=\"anchor-553f974bcdd29882\" style=\"position: relative;\">1. 动机<a href=\"#anchor-553f974bcdd29882\" aria-label=\"anchor 553f974bcdd29882 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>进行 <strong>图增强(graph augmentation)</strong> 的动机：输入图很难恰好是适宜于 GNN 的最优计算图。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>特征层面：\n<ul>\n<li>输入图可能缺少特征</li>\n<li>特征很难编码</li>\n<li>GNN 难以学习到特定的图结构</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>结构层面：\n<ul>\n<li>图过度稀疏：message passing 效率太低——增加虚拟节点/边</li>\n<li>图过度稠密：message passing 代价太高——对邻居抽样</li>\n<li>图太大：放不进 GPU——在 embedding 时对子图抽样</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-7ce2cbbbaaad8fa8\" style=\"position: relative;\">2. 图特征增强<a href=\"#anchor-7ce2cbbbaaad8fa8\" aria-label=\"anchor 7ce2cbbbaaad8fa8 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-832a3881b59cfafe\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1. 图缺少节点特征<a href=\"#anchor-832a3881b59cfafe\" aria-label=\"anchor 832a3881b59cfafe permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>constant node feature：给所有点赋相同常量作为特征。所有点的特征是相同的，但是 GNN 仍然可以从图结构中学到信息。</li>\n<li>one-hot node feature：给每个点分配编号，并编码成 one-hot 向量。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/08/30/o2smfZD7.png\"alt=\"o2smfZD7.png\" style=\"width: 603px; \" ></p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-9099aad53b9af579\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2. GNN 难以学习特定图结构<a href=\"#anchor-9099aad53b9af579\" aria-label=\"anchor 9099aad53b9af579 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>多元环的计算图都是二叉树，无法进行区分。类似的问题在特定图结构上也会出现。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/08/30/74MVmsYr.png\"alt=\"74MVmsYr.png\" style=\"width: 600px; \" ></p>\n<p>需要把此类图结构特征给编码到节点当中（可以加一维也可以是添加一个 one-hot 向量）。常用的有：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>cycle count（所在环的大小）</li>\n<li>节点度数</li>\n<li>clustering coefficient</li>\n<li>centrality</li>\n<li>PageRank</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-7834ee01a6f48aee\" style=\"position: relative;\">3. 图结构增强<a href=\"#anchor-7834ee01a6f48aee\" aria-label=\"anchor 7834ee01a6f48aee permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-504cc033cfc2c5f1\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.1. 稀疏图的结构增强<a href=\"#anchor-504cc033cfc2c5f1\" aria-label=\"anchor 504cc033cfc2c5f1 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>在 2-hop 邻居之间添加虚拟边（在 GNN 计算时不用 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span></span>，而是用 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>A</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A+A^{2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>），适用于 <strong>二分图(bipartite graph)</strong> 等。</li>\n<li>添加一个虚拟节点，该节点与图上所有节点都有边。这将导致所有节点之间的最长距离变为 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span></span></span>，从而大幅提高信息传递的效率。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-7dc0a51037de4d0e\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.2. 稠密图的结构增强<a href=\"#anchor-7dc0a51037de4d0e\" aria-label=\"anchor 7dc0a51037de4d0e permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>在传播时对邻居节点进行抽样。</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-578b31171719ea62\" style=\"position: relative;\">4. 参考资料<a href=\"#anchor-578b31171719ea62\" aria-label=\"anchor 578b31171719ea62 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://snap.stanford.edu/class/cs224w-2020/slides/08-GNN-application.pdf\">08-GNN-application.pdf (stanford.edu)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/PolarisRisingWar/article/details/118001121\">cs224w（图机器学习）2021 冬季课程学习笔记 10 Applications of Graph Neural Networks_在 2-hop 邻居之间增加虚拟边-CSDN 博客</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-553f974bcdd29882\">1. 动机</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-7ce2cbbbaaad8fa8\">2. 图特征增强</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-832a3881b59cfafe\">2.1. 图缺少节点特征</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-9099aad53b9af579\">2.2. GNN 难以学习特定图结构</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-7834ee01a6f48aee\">3. 图结构增强</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-504cc033cfc2c5f1\">3.1. 稀疏图的结构增强</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-7dc0a51037de4d0e\">3.2. 稠密图的结构增强</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-578b31171719ea62\">4. 参考资料</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"图增强","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation/","isDoc":true,"category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"3d3472ba-4912-5781-8d34-e29c88684305","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":"[{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/index.md\",\"title\":\"Intro\"},{\"title\":\"Notes\",\"children\":[{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/graph-neural-networks\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/graph-neural-networks.md\",\"title\":\"图神经网络\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation.md\",\"title\":\"图增强\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/knowledge-graph\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/knowledge-graph.md\",\"title\":\"知识图谱\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/subgraph-mining\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/subgraph-mining.md\",\"title\":\"子图挖掘\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/community-detection\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/community-detection.md\",\"title\":\"社区发现\"}]}]"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}